Project Bureau — ATF1504BE Logic Block D Interconnect Muxes

Project Bureau aims at documenting the bitstream format of Microchip ATF15xx CPLDs. This is a work in progress. See more in the repository

Interconnect Mux Configuration Bitmap

Logic block D uses 360 (known) fuses within range 32640..34080 for interconnect muxes UIM2, UIM3, UIM6, UIM7, UIM10, UIM11, UIM14, UIM15, UIM18, UIM19, UIM22, UIM23, UIM26, UIM27, UIM30, UIM31, UIM34, UIM35, UIM38, UIM39, UIM42, UIM43, UIM46, UIM47, UIM50, UIM51, UIM54, UIM55, UIM58, UIM59, UIM62, UIM63, UIM66, UIM67, UIM70, UIM71, UIM74, UIM75, UIM78, UIM79.
